---
title: Zucchini, Lemon and Chicken Breast Linguine with Basil Pesto and Goat Cheese
description: We love zucchini all year long here at HelloFresh, and this dish combines some of our favourite flavours: sweet snap peas, zucchini and basil pesto. A little squeeze of lemon at the end brings the whole dish together!
